########################################################################################################################
dataLoader.py  :: preprocessing data, return cleaned message list and label
nblearn.py     :: training NB model, build up P(word|ham) P(word|spam) table
nbclassify.py  :: testing NB model, return accuracy, TF,TN,FP,FN
main.py        :: __main__ file, train, test model and output results




e.g running:
python main.py SMSSpamCollection

sys.argv[1] takes data file path